        &kp UNDERSCORE  &kp MINUS     &kp LEFT_PARENTHESIS  &kp RIGHT_PARENTHESIS  &kp GRAVE        &kp EQUAL     &kp LESS_THAN  &kp GREATER_THAN  &kp SQT          &trans
&trans  &kp AT_SIGN     &trans        &kp LEFT_BRACKET      &kp RIGHT_BRACKET      &kp COLON        &kp QUESTION  &kp HASH       &kp COLON         &kp EXCLAMATION  &trans  &trans
                                      &trans                &trans                 &trans           &trans        &trans         &trans
