        navigation {
            bindings = <
        &trans  &trans  &kp C_VOL_DN  &kp C_VOLUME_UP  &trans    &trans  &trans    &kp UP_ARROW    &trans     &trans
        &trans  &trans  &trans        &trans           &trans    &trans  &kp LEFT  &kp DOWN_ARROW  &kp RIGHT  &trans
